author: COMSOL
description:
This model represents a test case of a flow in an elastic tube. This specific case models viscoelastic flow and represents steady flow in a channel in which part of the upper wall is replaced by an elastic plate subjected to an external pressure. The model reproduces the results reported in the literature.

NOTE: The model requires the Polymer Flow Module and the Structural Mechanics Module.
